reviewText: 'poor sound, mediocre visual, no speaking in-between songs (or any interviews either).  It was only entertaining because Eddie and Sammy are talented.  'unfortunate that this was the ONLY option on Amazon (that I could find) for a Van Halen concert.  I remember MUCH better, first hand, from back in the day.

Seems like every song these guys write are gold!!These videos are awesome, Sammy Hagar was a great replacement for David Lee Roth,both are excellent performers,Van Hagar music is awesome,greatest rock band ever,can't get enough!! Rock on forever!!!!
The product was everything I was hoping for! Them days were when music rocked and people had fun at concerts!
